account.

begin working correctly again.

<//dashboard.privy.com/settings/accounts#linked-account-heading-393761> 
  Here are some common reasons for this error: Here are some common reasons
for this error:

  - Revoking permissions granted to Privy.
  - Uninstalling Privy.
  - The end of a trial account.
  - Attempting to do anything with this linked account will fail since
Privy cannot connect to it.
  - All campaigns that are connected to this linked account will not
automatically sync contacts until the issue is resolved.

won't see any visual difference.

synced.
